results.title: In the Clutches of the God-Eater!
A Gazetteer of Asgard and Environs
The Blood of Dawn
results.description: Giants kill the wife of Odin's banished son and Odin sends Thor along with Vidar to enact their vengenance.

results.title: And Evil Shall Inherit
results.description: Mephisto captures Ulik's brother and forces him to fight Thor as ransome.

results.title: The Return of the Thermal Man
"The Origin of ""The Once And Future"" Thor"
The House of M
results.description: What changes await Steve Rogers life now that the House of M is in control? In this new world order, watch the hero known as Captain America moves from the '40s to the present day, bearing witness to a changing landscape, watching as man becomes the minority, and mutant the ruler. [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 3 of 6
results.description: The Winter Soldier storyline continues its relentless assault on the very soul of Steve Rogers! Who is the Winter Soldier, and how did he come to be one of the most effective weapons of the Cold War? In this haunting issue, Cap learns the answers to those questions and more. But the answers he receives may make what he has to do next even harder. [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 4 of 6
results.description: Part Four of the trail-blazing Winter Soldier arc hits hard! Cap now knows the truth about the Winter Soldier, and it's far worse than he could have imagined. Now, lost in this torment, he faces a long dark night of the soul, while on the other side of the world, General Lukin's plans for the Cosmic Cube finally come to light... But is he using the cube, or is the cube using him? [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 5 of 6
results.description: As "The Winter Soldier" arc rockets toward its senses-shattering conclusion, Cap's allies come to his aid in the hunt for the man he believes may actually be his one-time partner. Featuring special guest appearances by both Iron Man and the Falcon! You can't miss this issue, as red-hot creative team Brubaker and Epting up the ante one more time. [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 6 of 6
results.description: Cap faces down his personal demons, in a hand-to-hand battle with the Winter Soldier. But he's not just fighting for victory, he's in a struggle for the heart and soul of everything he's ever cared about, and the results will send tragic echoes throughout his life for years to come! [per solicitation]

results.title: Red is the Darkest Color
results.description: Six months ago, Crossbones kidnapped the Red Skull's daughter from a government reeducation facility, and disappeared into the night. Now learn where they have been all this time, and what his plans are for this spawn of infinite evil. [per solicitations]

results.title: Collision Courses Part 1 of 2
results.description: Crossbones has manipulated the Red Skull's daughter into a killing machine. Opening of the story has them both on a graphic killing spree. Captain America and Sharon Carter are on the trail of Bucky Barnes. Agents of A.I.M. confront Steve Rogers and Sharon in bed asking for their help. For what?

results.title: Collision Courses Part 2 of 2
results.description: Crossbones and the Red Skull's daughter, Sin, have come to the American Midwest to tear a new hole in A.I.M., but none of them counted on Cap and S.H.I.E.L.D. Agent 13 stumbling into the mix, and everything going wrong. The action-packed conclusion of this two-parter will leave two vengeance-fueled characters on a collision course with destiny and destruction!

results.title: Twenty-First Century Blitz Part One
results.description: Captain America travels across the Atlantic in search of his old partner, a story that will see him fighting side-by-side with some very old friends. But Cap and the Winter Soldier aren’t the only ones taking the journey abroad, Crossbones and Sin are on a path of revenge that’s leading them in the exact same direction... And what of General Lukin and his “relationship” with the Red Skull?

results.title: Twenty-First Century Blitz!
results.description: Cap and Union Jack have stumbled onto a new enemy that turns out to be tougher than expected, while Spitfire tries to find out what the Kronas Corp. is constructing under the city... and while all this goes on, the Winter Soldier stalks his prey!

results.title: Out of Time, Part 2 of 6
results.description: Cap is awakened in the dead of the night by Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. who need the kind of help only he can provide. But the corpse he finds on the Heli-carrier brings him face-to-face with the unthinkable, and opens doors to terror and manipulation that he never dreamed possible. [per solicitation]

results.title: Twenty-First Century Blitz!
results.description: s the “Twenty-First Century Blitz” rips through the streets of London, Cap comes face-to-face with an enemy he last faced in World War Two. And with Union Jack and Spitfire at his side, he fights to save London from destruction, while the Red Skull makes his move!

results.title: Out of Time, Part 3 of 6
results.description: Pursuing the Red Skull's mysterious trail brings Cap and S.H.I.E.L.D. Agent Sharon Carter into a brutal crossfire between warring factions of A.I.M. What does one of these groups have to do with the Skull's evil plans? And, is it just their imagination, or are Sharon and Cap being followed? [per solicitation]

results.title: The Lonesome Death of Jack Monroe
results.description: Nomad is dead, struck down by the same hand that killed the Red Skull! Now in a special interlude issue, we step back into Jack Monroe's last days and trace his last steps. Where had Jack been all these years, and why was he drowning his sorrows in some dive bar? Also -- what did Jack see that night, right before he breathed his last? You'll be shocked to find out! [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 1 of 6
results.description: The questions plaguing Captain America's dreams and memories have been answered in the most brutal way possible. And in the wake of this brutality, General Lukin makes his first all-out assault! Our second arc tears open old wounds and threatens to make new scars that will never heal. [per solicitation]

results.title: The Winter Soldier, Part 2 of 6
results.description: Our second arc continues to cut a brutal swath through all that Captain America holds sacred. In the wake of disaster, Cap begins his hunt for the enemy that has dogged his steps, who has taken more from him than anyone ever has! [per solicitation]
